The paper also discusses the translation of weight constraints into nested expressions, which involves logical reasoning and manipulation, making it relevant to the sub-category of logic in computer science (cs.LO). The paper also deals with programming languages and their semantics, which falls under the sub-category of programming languages (cs.PL).
